file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Petstore
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: "https://{env}.localhost:{port}"
    variables:
      env:
        default: dev
        enum: ['dev', 'test', 'prod']
      port:
        default: "8080"
paths:
  /:
    get:
      tags: ["foo", "foo-bar"]
      operationId: list
      parameters:
        - in: header
          name: X-Callback-Url
          required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 200 response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: 
                type: string
  /test:
    get:
      tags: ["foo", "foo-bar"]
      operationId: getTest
      parameters:
        - in: header
          name: X-Callback-Url
          required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 200 response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: 
                type: string
  /{id}:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Address"
      responses:
        200:
          description: 200 response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: 
                type: string
components:
  schemas:
    Test:
      description: "Bla Bla"
      type: integer
      nullable: true
    Test2:
      allOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Test"
        - nullable: false
    Address:
      type: object
      required:
        - city
        - zip
        - street
        - lineOne
        - lineTwo
      properties:
        country:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        city:
          type: string
        street:
          type: string
          writeOnly: true
        lineOne:
          type: string
          readOnly: true
        lineTwo:
          type: string
          readOnly: true
    OneOfDiscriminatedNormal:
      oneOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Address"
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Test2"
      discriminator:
        propertyName: type
    OneOfDiscriminatedDefined:
      oneOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Address"
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Test2"
      discriminator:
        propertyName: type
        mapping:
          one: '#/components/schemas/Address'
          two: '#/components/schemas/Test2'
    OneOfUndiscriminated:
      oneOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Address"
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Test2"
